text:
Disappointing, encountered an absolutely rude cashier. Fair skin guy wearing black specs. More interested to check his mobile phone than to work.
Food is below average as the guy wasn’t interested to cook.
Their food was GOOD!! Such affordable price with good western food! Tasty, delicious and generous serving! I have been a regular patron for the past one year, their food never disappoints!

Ordered for delivery and beef burger looks like the fake ones you get at pasar malam. I understand perhaps that’s why it’s that price point, but I’m also not expecting this and would very much prefer to have paid slightly more for a single decent beef patty. The fish and chips are good though but both the wedges and the fries were underwhelming. Wedges tasted dry and has a weird colour to it. The star is the pan fried mushrooms which are nicely seasoned and fresh. The mushroom soup also looks like instant mix and just adding some mushrooms into them. Probably wouldn’t order again.

Order their western food from food panda and The chicken cutlet and lamp chop was very black… seriously overcook (chao da) and dry… didn’t dare to eat but just end up throwing it away.. dont think ill order from them ever again :(

Didn't order for quite a while so today decided to order their food. My hb placed order thru WA and also called them to confirm the order. That ah soh damn attitude! kept telling him she's busy! When I reached there, I told her the order no last 4D, she kept asking me to re-order and told me she's busy! Since so busy then don't take order via WA lah! Common sense leh... if I re-order, isn't it there will be duplicate order?!!! From a happy mood looking forward to their food, now become no mood to eat! KNS!
